Well written gritty police series set in beautiful scenic western Ireland.  Story lines deal with corruption, deal-making, insidious city crime in a small town, arson, drug smuggling and family conflicts.  Watched two series ... wish there were more.  Good acting, great locales, slight romance, plenty of conflict and lots more room for more episodes.
Small town policing - blurred ethical lines!
